# Claude Agent Demo Deployment Package

## Files to Deploy:

### 1. Demo Page
- `src/app/claude-agent-demo/page.tsx` - Main demo UI with real-time logs

### 2. API Endpoint  
- `src/app/api/claude-agent-demo/execute/route.ts` - Streaming API for Claude Agent execution

### 3. Dependencies Required
```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "next": "^14.0.0",
    "react": "^18.0.0", 
    "react-dom": "^18.0.0",
    "@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk": "latest",
    "tailwindcss": "^3.0.0",
    "lucide-react": "^0.263.1"
  }
}
```

### 4. Environment Variables
```bash
NEO4J_URI=your-neo4j-uri
NEO4J_USERNAME=neo4j
NEO4J_PASSWORD=your-password
BRIGHTDATA_API_TOKEN=your-token
BRIGHTDATA_ZONE=linkedin_posts_monitor
PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=your-key
```

## Deployment Commands:

```bash
# On server
mkdir -p /home/ubuntu/claude-agent-demo
cd /home/ubuntu/claude-agent-demo

# Upload files from local machine:
scp -i yellowpanther.pem -r src/ ubuntu@13.60.60.50:/home/ubuntu/claude-agent-demo/

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run demo
npm run dev
```

